notes.title: Data Availability
notes.p: The data utilized in this study are from the NYS STI and HIV Surveillance Registries ( https://www.health.ny.gov/statistics/diseases/communicable/std/docs/sti_surveillance_report_2017.pdf; https://www.health.ny.gov/diseases/aids/general/statistics/annual/2017/2017_annual_surveillance_report.pdf). Due to legal restrictions enacted to protect patient confidentiality, direct access to the data is prohibited. Interested parties may direct requests to the Bureau of Sexual Health and Epidemiology, AIDS Institute, New York State Department of Health, ESP Corning Tower, Albany, NY; Tele: 518-474-3598, email: STDC@health.ny.gov.
